How to control servo using MPU6050 Gyroscope with Arduino（Breadboard Leonardo）
      舵机与MPU6050结合
      输出  X Y Z
      晃动  MPU6050 控制舵机转动

      MPU6050 Wiring:
      SCL – A5
      SDA – A4
      VCC – 3.3V
      GND – GND 
      INT – PIN3

      Servo Wiring:
      VCC – 5V
      GND – GND 
      Control - PIN3
      伺机库 https://github.com/jrowberg/i2cdevlib
      视频    https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vSKEH0FwhUE
      程式码  https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B0SU0douW9lVenJ0Vng0QlEyUDQ/view

Controlling a Servo with an Arduino and MPU6050
      VCC 5V 
      GND GND 
      SCL A5 
      SDA A4
      视频https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sOE8AjJ3gvQ
